bic coupling for strongly coupled models. The upcoming\n14 TeV run of the LHC will stringently test this scenario and we identify\nseveral new searches with discovery potential for this class of models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Nov 2014 21:11:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
