rene has been electrically tuned\nover a large spectral range at room temperature, which opens a new route for\ntunable light sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Nov 2014 12:29:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-25"}
